人知佢滑雪優惠套票有冇限買幾多張？<br />\n<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇限日數<br />\n我用左兩日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728f8f646c3f14ed562721246e05cf412f8b9430","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2月我都會去呢度滑<br />\n上次去過次，但直接去滑雪場買正價算數無咁煩<br />\n反而租雪具．我去咗第二個地方度租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外想問如果連租幾日係咪可以自己keep住唔洗還返俾佢先？"},{"pid":"1a61aa2fef4ea8bd5fa96ee88068e484fde7bb20","tid":53820,"uid":35560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:41:26.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\n係東京過去車錢來回一個人都成千蚊 <br />\n租車會唔會方便d<br />\n落雪既話架車洗唔洗換軑或者做咩防滑架？<br />\n同埋轉日本車牌會唔會好多野搞？"},{"pid":"a7aeea6520751448cc00857109ec1dd645e561f1","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問<br />\n係東京過去車錢來回一個人都成千蚊 <br />\n租車會唔會方便d<br />\n落雪既話架車洗唔洗換軑或者做咩防滑架？<br />\n同埋轉日本車牌會唔會好多野搞？</blockquote><br />\n新幹線一個鐘直達門口<br />\n租車一定唔會快過鐵路啦<br />\n張3日pass先10000yen圍返先7舊唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會仲揸車，除非你有乜特別地方想去？"},{"pid":"bcde37dd703567a8c0e7f064de02eb4e2cc8f27b","tid":53820,"uid":46636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"5號去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係官網買早鳥入場券"},{"pid":"c9ec31bdf4e41fbe0bd3d42fbc8e66d4aa6261d9","tid":53820,"uid":6414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"1月中去<img src=\"/assets/faces