edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T08:19:40.000Z","msg":"買板係咪多數都去御茶之水買？"},{"pid":"47a5db24201e461f6eb7eb8df1a9aeb867e0cb34","tid":53820,"uid":6414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買板係咪多數都去御茶之水買？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n剩係喺嗰到買過吉他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105f27ee13e323b1a3d67c32e25fe10121088382","tid":53820,"uid":45928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買板係咪多數都去御茶之水買？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果第一次玩就係 gala 租，用jr pass 有優惠<br />\n試下先下次先買<br />\n<br />\n講開御茶之水，果幾間賣體育用品好鬼雜貨場 feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a140331d266e9773515ab4db51cc896276ad8d2c","tid":53820,"uid":71358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T11:05:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gala 新手滑道有一條唔斜又闊<br />\n如果玩 ski 仆多幾次就可以一 take 過唔跌<br />\n<br />\n唔搵教練學都得，不過要睇下 YouTube 教學片<br />\n最小要識跌倒丶起身丶減速等</blockquote><br />\n想問問個場會唔會好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nGala應該最多人，附近其實仲有幾個場。上星期去咗神樂兩日，個場玩SB都好正，但啲雪都係未夠粉<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9VN6s6J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9VN6s6J.jpg&h=18d45bd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66d73f95255cc93e8b2f823db711c4d17f4ac175","tid":53820,"uid":6550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T19:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2月我都會去呢度滑<br />\n上次去過次，但直接去滑雪場買正價算數無咁煩<br />\n反而租雪具．我去咗第二個地方度租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年4個人租兩日，剩係塊板既價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/02/032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F02%2F032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg&h=8dafc234&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5ab5086b34066a7dba81f51bf8a75ca6a116918","tid":53820,"uid":6550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T19:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2月我都會去呢度滑<br />\n上次去過次，但直接去滑雪場買正價算數無咁煩<br />\n反而租雪具．我去咗第二個地方度租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外想問如果連租幾日係咪可以自己keep住唔洗還返俾佢先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗的，你滑完打返佢比你既電話，佢會車你返店鋪，第2日再由酒店車你去店再拎返板再車去滑雪場"},{"pid":"520183de096da794dbb8fd2da73ebf466f2e429b","tid":53820,"uid":6550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T19:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85d6O13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85d6O13.jpg&h=6155ba6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間酒店一流"},{"pid":"828bdb62e68b1f1db4393f7ea80f9ae1cfc1f34f","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T01:11:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2月我都會去呢度滑<br />\n上次去過次，但直接去滑雪場買正價算數無咁煩<br />\n反而租雪具．我去咗第二個地方度租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年4個人租兩日，剩係塊板既價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/02/032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F02%2F032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg&h=8dafc234&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n400yen 2日咁撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁鞋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"25de19f9f1d1885bbbc1542c757724dda7c4f447","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T01:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2月我都會去呢度滑<br />\n上次去過次，但直接去滑雪場買正價算數無咁煩<br />\n反而租雪具．我去咗第二個地方度租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外想問如果連租幾日係咪可以自己keep住唔洗還返俾佢先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗的，你滑完打返佢比你既電話，佢會車你返店鋪，第2日再由酒店車你去店再拎返板再車去滑雪場</blockquote><br />\n想問你係上湯澤高原滑定gala滑？見間野係湯澤高原下面<br />\n我book左酒店係越後湯澤站隔離，滑就諗住去gala<br />\n<br />\n可以係佢度租完然後叫佢接送去gala？<br />\n滑完可以call返佢黎接？<br />\n另外想問係咪要日文溝通？<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7f7999143690bee6af6c58e8a211efe2aac0fe","tid":53820,"uid":954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"7 號 8 號 去 👋"},{"pid":"7c85b2db5fe06de0149a6ac0a6b1d76482fd2ccb","tid":53820,"uid":6550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年4個人租兩日，剩係塊板既價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/02/032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F02%2F032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg&h=8dafc234&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n400yen 2日咁撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁鞋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連埋"},{"pid":"03f06eae5df66a6eaab1146b5a35439a7a9304d8","tid":53820,"uid":6550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T02:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外想問如果連租幾日係咪可以自己keep住唔洗還返俾佢先？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔洗的，你滑完打返佢比你既電話，佢會車你返店鋪，第2日再由酒店車你去店再拎返板再車去滑雪場</blockquote><br />\n想問你係上湯澤高原滑定gala滑？見間野係湯澤高原下面<br />\n我book左酒店係越後湯澤站隔離，滑就諗住去gala<br />\n<br />\n可以係佢度租完然後叫佢接送去gala？<br />\n滑完可以call返佢黎接？<br />\n另外想問係咪要日文溝通？<br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以車去gala ,我上次都係咁<br />\n用英文溝通就得，簡單英文可以<br />\n個老闆識英文"},{"pid":"83fecb3cbd33622889dfc54e1be51886b125e13f","tid":53820,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:23:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gala.co.jp/winter/access_bus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgala.co.jp%2Fwinter%2Faccess_bus.html&d=gtlVt1sD%2B290nI6en9BbUksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=bd069766\" target=\"_blank\">https://gala.co.jp/winter/access_bus.html</a><br />\n<br />\n雪場通常有shuttle 去附近地區"},{"pid":"b880475d11ed579233735067342ce0ca95664c8f","tid":53820,"uid":58374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"搭單問<br />\n張 pass 係咪可以搭埋去迪迪尼"},{"pid":"caf3870a4e455bdacbd76ccc58c0c3781b536559","tid":53820,"uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4408f67bda976916ff779664470048e3f6bd0a8d","tid":53820,"uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5lqzxgav\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5lqzxgav&h=9c385b8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22eb768a40d5a5509d3f5f7de58c3c606c923e1a","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年4個人租兩日，剩係塊板既價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/02/032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F02%2F032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg&h=8dafc234&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n400yen 2日咁撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁鞋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連埋</blockquote><br />\n點解我係個網見到要2500 yen一日既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fedcdf930b684693769ed52b423e551ea800e8f1","tid":53820,"uid":26224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2月我都會去呢度滑<br />\n上次去過次，但直接去滑雪場買正價算數無咁煩<br />\n反而租雪具．我去咗第二個地方度租</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年4個人租兩日，剩係塊板既價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/02/032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F02%2F032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg&h=8dafc234&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩緊，係個場租要 73xx yen 2日。<br />\n巴打，你咁平，有無水資料或網址？"},{"pid":"a4b16279ce90e98222b5cdcf7413c6d23f095ab1","tid":53820,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T03:49:49.000Z","msg":"雪場入邊租一定貴D。週圍同洒店格下價。同埋初學唔洗租太靚板<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日好似溫澤7度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cfe242e078e07a6d48e321ad875a0af5fcd91c","tid":53820,"uid":37966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n400yen 2日咁撚平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁鞋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連埋</blockquote><br />\n點解我係個網見到要2500 yen一日既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 點解可以咁平？ 我九號滑啦 有無板同衫的好推介？"},{"pid":"1225fb1d4f000ebf19e2e835d091cc602c499b1f","tid":53820,"uid":6550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T12:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇邊度租雪具平可以介紹？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年4個人租兩日，剩係塊板既價錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/02/032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F02%2F032459_9a300c3ba0ab4279e3928b6e362edb2e.jpg&h=8dafc234&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩緊，係個場租要 73xx yen 2日。<br />\n巴打，你咁平，有無水資料或網址？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以因爲酒店同個間租滑板間野係合作之類"},{"pid":"96c3b505c17f62a03d9e560a825e4d19ecb6bede","tid":53820,"uid":6550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連埋</blockquote><br />\n點解我係個網見到要2500 yen一日既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 點解可以咁平？ 我九號滑啦 有無板同衫的好推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n板佢會按你身高同體重來比塊板你，無咩所謂<br />\n我上次第一次滑，無上堂，自學左幾粒鐘，最緊要唔好怕pk<br />\n<br />\n原本係打算滑兩日，點知第一日滑完，累到hihi，第二日cancel 左，租板個間野仲好人到退返第二日租板既錢比我地，心諗以為要自己去拎錢，反而係佢地專人送返錢來我間酒店度"},{"pid":"854f65d3d1cb296dca38da90808870ad96e584e9","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連埋</blockquote><br />\n點解我係個網見到要2500 yen一日既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 點解可以咁平？ 我九號滑啦 有無板同衫的好推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n板佢會按你身高同體重來比塊板你，無咩所謂<br />\n我上次第一次滑，無上堂，自學左幾粒鐘，最緊要唔好怕pk<br />\n<br />\n原本係打算滑兩日，點知第一日滑完，累到hihi，第二日cancel 左，租板個間野仲好人到退返第二日租板既錢比我地，心諗以為要自己去拎錢，反而係佢地專人送返錢來我間酒店度</blockquote><br />\n間野咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415a7d109161ff31c93a9b96d7fcd43c7f3e0b79","tid":53820,"uid":71358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-02T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n點解我係個網見到要2500 yen一日既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 點解可以咁平？ 我九號滑啦 有無板同衫的好推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n板佢會按你身高同體重來比塊板你，無咩所謂<br />\n我上次第一次滑，無上堂，自學左幾粒鐘，最緊要唔好怕pk<br />\n<br />\n原本係打算滑兩日，點知第一日滑完，累到hihi，第二日cancel 左，租板個間野仲好人到退返第二日租板既錢比我地，心諗以為要自己去拎錢，反而係佢地專人送返錢來我間酒店度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實第二日先係主菜，個肌肉開始識放鬆，滑嗰陣先叫漸入佳境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485d921f6fff342a96a54a6734014378d4251f16","tid":53820,"uid":25205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T01:41:11.000Z","msg":"留名 <br />\n<br />\n11號去滑4日"},{"pid":"c21a19acfa7c2b7928ae37d40a034898d3764ad2","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T02:07:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 <br />\n<br />\n11號去滑4日</blockquote><br />\n18號去滑3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0054ffe8f24d13b1d92f6bfe9fc6be3a04e397ad","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T12:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec080e6090aa54661f1b95d19676d39e55153bd","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-04T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5dba787a109aa649102fa94e7466de540c0862","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T03:22:20.000Z","msg":"想問你地保險會買邊份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見藍十字寫明包滑雪"},{"pid":"ee2b973cde1f065b6db331f34a5b33e714132bcf","tid":53820,"uid":56280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"四月中會揸車上湯澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲建唔建議加雪胎?"},{"pid":"e52dd714321fd7722ea820e844dbb9874af3852d","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四月中會揸車上湯澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲建唔建議加雪胎?</blockquote><br />\n要，4月山區仲有雪"},{"pid":"7d4e842b2b89bd8681916b4e7581b092fc134d00","tid":53820,"uid":56280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T07:43:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>四月中會揸車上湯澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲建唔建議加雪胎?</blockquote><br />\n要，4月山區仲有雪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過雪胎好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打你租gear 會去邊度租?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6706c087539a3718f4e5fce8fb83326522b9f9f","tid":53820,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-12T08:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>四月中會揸車上湯澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下咁多位巴絲建唔建議加雪胎?</blockquote><br />\n要，4月山區仲有雪</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過雪胎好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁巴打你租gear 會去邊度租?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你指雪胎定鍊？<br />\n雪胎唔係基本配備咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我記得去洞爺湖租車都有得揀普通胎定雪胎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝備去左上面巴打講果間租，已予約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a6dca856d11aec17a2d1975e4649c9712fb70d","tid":53820,"uid":6414,"like":0,"dislik